{"tid":278653,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"專名號是咪已經收咗皮","createTime":"2017-06-10T15:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T08:37:56.000Z","uid":118314,"like":178,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ca0496a7098924905835fb0c2bbc94045c712b7","tid":278653,"uid":118314,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:32:03.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇post (小學時比人教錯知識果個)<br />\n見到有人post小學測驗卷，見到D國家名下面要加一劃，<br />\n我先醒起有樣咁嘅野，仲要google咗一陣先記得番佢叫專名號 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但到頭嚟出到社會所有文件其實根本都唔會用專名號，<br />\n到底教嚟做乜野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知而家教科書是咪仲會教 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9cfc08b89579e5e1d6d5f405b676181d59f6639","tid":278653,"uid":36435,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:34:46.000Z","msg":"仲有書名號"},{"pid":"8a338453655c0772fee020c20c88e45ecbb2ebbd","tid":278653,"uid":1139,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5fe3549e4a1bba3b06f856a6f10e3ae84f3bcc6d","tid":278653,"uid":710,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有書名號</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n書名號都會用下"},{"pid":"3b2ed0e0ced62d2947c39835d2dc17e71e0e018e","tid":278653,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有書名號</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實電腦打唔打得出書名號"},{"pid":"acea1f26f1d3fc29ccac797cdefb40bd798746fd","tid":278653,"uid":118314,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:36:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有書名號</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實電腦打唔打得出書名號</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係打到，但我都唔記得個碼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efce983876c01acf9ef67c5981a7ccf51094ff0","tid":278653,"uid":78039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有書名號</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n書名號都會用下</blockquote><br />\n由蛇仔變咗《》"},{"pid":"a091d345a9180a3d6e49e0b8c7c0fe238eb3f8e8","tid":278653,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:37:41.000Z","msg":"其實《》係咪畫名號 蛇仔係咪收左皮"},{"pid":"30ba8092c203ef8d72b11dad48179fb16b39d2f8","tid":278653,"uid":78039,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實《》係咪畫名號 蛇仔係咪收左皮</blockquote><br />\n﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏"},{"pid":"604f2822bca2232605e4587a2224ff0d8f399ea8","tid":278653,"uid":20736,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:38:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有書名號</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n書名號都會用下</blockquote><br />\n由蛇仔變咗《》</blockquote><br />\n但細個記得老師話大陸先用呢個<br />\n香港要用蛇仔<br />\n上到中學就發現無人用蛇仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同堆蛇仔易寫得好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a3ed1e8e14bb5eb1c990d4065c2e2c4f7b277c","tid":278653,"uid":78039,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實《》係咪畫名號 蛇仔係咪收左皮</blockquote><br />\n﹏﹏﹏係中華民國<br />\n《》係中華人民共和國"},{"pid":"86806abb970cfffbf8bd85f3cd0d20b102d878f4","tid":278653,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:40:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實《》係咪畫名號 蛇仔係咪收左皮</blockquote><br />\n﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以好似<ins>underline</ins>咁打出嚟咩"},{"pid":"5ec13368e01c35aa47de208f8b6b0282a357ca4f","tid":278653,"uid":8028,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:40:25.000Z","msg":"《》好似好睇啲"},{"pid":"67761b27e51fda28cc77a400a579c3c17c85d398","tid":278653,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:31:43.000Z","msg":"又係喎。真係已經十世無用"},{"pid":"67f21f04870e95bb1b2f93224